nclude/libgnome-2.0 -I/opt/local/include/libbonoboui-2.0 -I/o

which corresponds to the first 1024 characters. If I paste to xterm
(also running zsh), I get something like:

/usr/bin/gcc-4.0 -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -I. -I.. -DGNOMELOCALEDIR=3D\"/opt/local/s=
hare/locale\" -DGNOME_DESKTOP_SYSCONFDIR=3D\"/opt/local/etc\" -DGNOME_DESKT=
